Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.32,0:01:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.09,0:02:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#19         ちぃ，等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.90,0:02:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.51,0:02:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.31,0:02:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還真拼命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來他真的很擔心ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為本須和是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.52,0:02:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉避開顏面著地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.43,0:02:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.23,0:02:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.23,0:02:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.07,0:02:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,線索只有這些嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.07,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能確定她有去過書店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.04,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許之後被捲入某件事件…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.08,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是被人帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.55,0:02:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被帶走了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這個可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟那封附圖郵件的\N發信者有關的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打個岔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.75,0:02:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.69,0:03:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介意我參與這件事件的討論嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.19,0:03:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳發現什麼的話，請告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.46,0:03:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這也有可能\N與附圖郵件的發信者有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.27,0:03:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.41,0:03:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許有不特定的多數人\N已經認識了ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.38,0:03:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前您曾將ちぃ的事\N寫在電腦網站的BBS裡吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許看到那篇文章的某人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在街上看到ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為對她有興趣，所以帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，現在只能去找找看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.34,0:03:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有消息的話\N就跟絲茉茉聯絡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.58,0:04:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是本須和啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你那樣子\N應該是還沒找到她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.93,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.36,0:04:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為店裡關門了\N所以我就來這附近找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.50,0:04:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟商店街的人聊聊\N也許能得到點線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.34,0:04:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，要是我早點聯絡你就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你一起找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人一起找\N一定能比較快找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.85,0:04:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.15,0:04:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花店這邊我已經問過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.95,0:04:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，幫不上你的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.53,0:04:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，謝謝你\N謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長頭髮的電腦啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.44,0:04:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒看到耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.91,0:04:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒看到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問過其他人了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.69,0:05:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商店街只剩這附近而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過與其一間一間找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.39,0:05:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用電腦登錄在商店街的聯絡網上\N不會比較快嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用奇洛如的電腦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，植田先生你那裡\N現在好像沒有電腦了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.64,0:05:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你四處問問吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有線索我會再跟你聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請跟她聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在傳送絲茉茉的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.42,0:05:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我跟妳的電腦連線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.56,0:05:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都好\N有消息的話請馬上跟我連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.69,0:05:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.88,0:06:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然明白…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.28,0:06:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛剛的消息看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.45,0:06:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也許是被人帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.02,0:06:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在說不定感到很痛苦\N正遭到其他人的折騰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到這點我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是到這附近再找一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.07,0:06:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快接過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.74,0:06:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子終於答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我先告訴你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我現在沒那個心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.58,0:06:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦會感到疼痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到傷害的話\N她會感到痛苦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.84,0:07:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂電腦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.47,0:07:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒輸入程式的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.51,0:07:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不會感受到痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.01,0:07:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算輸入了痛覺的程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.68,0:07:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事後從硬碟與記憶體\N將它清除就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.22,0:07:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清除？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.26,0:07:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，將資料刪除\N就會變成什麼事都沒發生過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.29,0:07:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是痛苦或是悲傷\N全部都會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.70,0:07:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然長得像人\N但電腦仍舊是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，我這邊有消息的話\N我會再跟你聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別太著急啊，拜囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算我很擔心\N但ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.83,0:08:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介意跟我聊聊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.50,0:08:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解新保說的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我真不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.34,0:08:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且ちぃ之前\N應該也有過主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.44,0:08:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，因為ちぃ是電腦\N就算記憶消失了也不難理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.05,0:08:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我看到ちぃ時\N並不會這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我講話沒頭沒腦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.56,0:08:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾因為同樣的事\N而產生混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.74,0:08:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾與電腦結過婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛好就在那家店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那間店是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.98,0:09:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在奇洛如剛開店時\N遇見她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.16,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電器行推薦我買最新型  的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.73,0:09:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然每個都很漂亮\N但卻分辦不出有什麼不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.23,0:09:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我發現了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在店的角落裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掛著特價的牌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身上積了少許的灰塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問過店員才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是即將被丟棄的舊機種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.62,0:09:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻不知不覺將她買了回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在仔細詳讀使用手冊後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於將她給啟動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊…我叫植田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田弘康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田先生是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輸入完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.52,0:10:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田先生是我的主人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.92,0:10:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是的，請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.97,0:10:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在想想\N這應該算是一見鍾情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.70,0:10:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都充滿笑容與活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愉快時會安慰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生好事時會為我高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.75,0:10:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都陪伴在我身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.02,0:10:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在不知不覺中\N深深的愛上了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛上身為電腦的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.53,0:10:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我跟她求婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.64,0:11:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興地露出平常的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.24,0:11:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是真的跟電腦結婚未免…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法律上是不可行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這等於是實質上的婚姻關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.12,0:11:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且電腦也擁有\N財產的贈與及繼承權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.83,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你家人沒有反對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父母都過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.93,0:11:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也舉行了正式的婚禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.14,0:11:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備了新娘禮服\N在一間小餐廳裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時還被登在報紙上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.61,0:11:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然商店街的人們都冷眼看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我是幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.32,0:11:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能與她在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.69,0:11:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能讓她保持笑容的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.73,0:11:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時卻已經有徵兆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徵兆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.45,0:12:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她開始變得健忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.95,0:12:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將許多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.55,0:12:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始以為是我搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.86,0:12:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時她會想不起前一天的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.30,0:12:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記錯材料放置的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後越來越嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.50,0:12:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後連客人剛點的蛋糕種類\N都記不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.18,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然查過很多書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但卻還是不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我帶她到電器行時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.55,0:12:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬碟已經完全損毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要修理的話必須整個換掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.96,0:13:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.83,0:13:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換掉就能修好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.69,0:13:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，不過因為這是舊機種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許無法完全將資料轉移過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.67,0:13:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.04,0:13:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說會失去\N開機至今的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.01,0:13:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會失去記憶嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.08,0:13:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對她而言太殘忍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.35,0:13:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.08,0:13:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們感覺不到悲傷與痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.85,0:13:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會忘得一乾二淨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.39,0:13:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要她忘記與我的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點我說什麼也辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.03,0:13:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也去問過其他店家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.04,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就這樣將她帶回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫植田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田弘康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田先生是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輸入完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.40,0:14:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,植田先生是我的主人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.44,0:14:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過她變得更嚴重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.68,0:14:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連幾秒前的事都記不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.75,0:14:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.65,0:14:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.93,0:14:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.36,0:14:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.37,0:14:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.47,0:14:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此\N但我還是沒有帶她去修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.24,0:14:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算所剩無幾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.88,0:15:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然僅會偶而記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.05,0:15:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是不能讓她\N完全失去她與我的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.82,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，過了一陣子\N在一個下雨的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與她出門購物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.03,0:15:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時，她連過著日常生活\N都很困難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.83,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一不留意就不知道會發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.21,0:15:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想著她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直無法入睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.05,0:15:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是恍惚了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.07,0:16:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.35,0:16:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是連車子的危險性\N都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在我心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.13,0:17:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻彷彿是救了我一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.48,0:17:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她明明應該什麼都不知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一點都不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.58,0:17:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是認為她救了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在車禍後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.09,0:17:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我有將她帶回店家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.13,0:17:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻是全毀了\N已經無法啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表也嚴重受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然店家曾說\N如果偏好這種款式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.17,0:17:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我找同一機型  的看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但對我而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻還是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.65,0:17:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她是電腦\N也沒有生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但對我而言，她已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.59,0:18:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經沒有記憶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.30,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也什麼都感覺不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.83,0:18:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我卻還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.27,0:18:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的長相、聲音\N她的一舉一動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及她的快樂與悲傷的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都讓我無法忘懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.25,0:18:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和你也是這樣吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.99,0:18:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算ちぃ忘記了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.59,0:18:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和你還是會記得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓她感到痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不會忘記的，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.70,0:18:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.33,0:18:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些事不可能完全消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.24,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縱使從硬碟上被刪除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.74,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要本須和你還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要找回ちぃ才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.71,0:18:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.71,0:18:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知該從何找起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我一定會找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想她一定在等著你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.75,0:19:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定那是抓走ちぃ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.76,0:19:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.56,0:19:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！裕美！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不會回頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.53,0:19:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我在，她就不會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.77,0:19:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為聽說她跟我在一起\N只會感到悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.37,0:19:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認識裕美嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.85,0:20:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，現在還是先去找ちぃ吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.38,0:20:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個檔案是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.02,0:20:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我在自製機網站上寫的\N關於ちぃ的留言的讀取記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.39,0:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他幫我寄來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.39,0:20:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真多虧他願意寄來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的站長欠我一份情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.23,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.27,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這與圖片傳送者作比對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.77,0:20:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個一個找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ這次會不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.24,0:20:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是因為我沒有考慮周詳\N就在站上提起她所引起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.78,0:20:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我講了不該講的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.99,0:20:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.99,0:20:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳讓我想到了另一種可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想跟妳道謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.97,0:20:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.17,0:21:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想姊姊應該也會\N做同樣的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.71,0:21:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.84,0:21:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊的確會溫柔地提醒我\N我看錯或是沒注意到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.49,0:21:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以會高興，並不是因為\N柚姬做出跟姊姊同樣的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.53,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.86,0:21:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.57,0:21:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.47,0:21:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這與之前寄來ちぃ的\N圖片郵件的帳號相同！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.68,0:21:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來裕美認識植田店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.88,0:21:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是裕美從沒提過此事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.26,0:21:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，現在得趕快找到ちぃ才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.40,0:22:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.50,0:22:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.91,0:22:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.95,0:22:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.13,0:22:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.20,0:23:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.89,0:23:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.36,0:23:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.34,0:23:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心痛         也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.02,0:23:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠         直到永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.70,0:23:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天也在尋找只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.70,0:23:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我，而喜歡上我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.87,0:23:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我無法實現夢想\N也會喜歡我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.01,0:23:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對ちぃ而言，特別的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.75,0:24:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「ちぃ，追求」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.79,0:24:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的…只屬於ちぃ的人
